    <briefdescription>
<para>This class implements the <ref refid="class_hd_embree_primvar_sampler" kindref="compound">HdEmbreePrimvarSampler</ref> interface for primvars on triangle meshes with &quot;vertex&quot; or &quot;varying&quot; interpolation modes. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This means the buffer has one item per vertex, and the result of sampling is a barycentric interpolation of the hit face vertices. This class requires the triangulated mesh topology, to map from the triangle index (in &quot;element&quot;) to the triangle vertices. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
